entries.title: Teacher shot by pupil, 6, 'showing signs of improvement' in hospital
entries.description: A teacher who was critically injured when she was shot by a six-year-old pupil in the US is showing signs of improvement, authorities say.

entries.title: Ukrainian families with loved ones on frontline mark Orthodox Christmas - and use TikTok to stay in touch
entries.description: In the gloom of her kitchen, Halyna Bereznitska prepares the Christmas meal.

entries.title: Six journalists held over video of president 'wetting himself'
entries.description: Six journalists have been detained after a video surfaced appearing to show the president of South Sudan wetting himself.

entries.title: NASA satellite to fall to Earth after 38 years in space
entries.description: A NASA satellite is expected to fall to Earth this weekend after nearly 40 years in space.

entries.title: Man dupes authors out of hundreds of unpublished manuscripts
entries.description: A man has admitted to stealing more than 1,000 unpublished manuscripts from distinguished authors said to include Ian McEwan, Margaret Atwood and Sally Rooney.

entries.title: Iran executes two more men over alleged protest violence
entries.description: Two men have been executed for allegedly killing a paramilitary volunteer during protests, Iranian authorities have said.

entries.title: Kevin McCarthy finally wins US Speaker vote after tensions boil over in chaotic Congress scenes
entries.description: Republican Kevin McCarthy has been elected as the new US Speaker after winning the 15th vote following chaotic scenes in Congress.

entries.title: McCarthy elected US Speaker at 15th attempt after tensions boil over in Congress
entries.description: Republican Kevin McCarthy has been elected as the new US Speaker after winning the 15th vote as tensions boiled over in Congress.

entries.title: Six-year-old boy shoots teacher during 'altercation' inside US classroom
entries.description: A six-year-old boy has left a teacher with life-threatening injuries after shooting her inside a classroom, US police have said.
